article.headline: Mashburn scores 26, Temple downs UMass 87-80
article.description: — Jamal Mashburn Jr. had 26 points in Temple's 87-80 victory against UMass on Saturday night.
article.story: UNCASVILLE, Conn. -- — Jamal Mashburn Jr. had 26 points in Temple's 87-80 victory against UMass on Saturday night. Mashburn shot 9 for 20 (2 for 4 from 3-point range) and 6 of 9 from the free-throw line for the Owls (4-2). Quante Berry scored 12 points and added six rebounds. William Settle had 12 points and shot 2 of 5 from the field and 8 for 12 from the line. Jaylen Curry led the Minutemen (1-4) in scoring, finishing with 17 points. UMass also got 15 points and 10 rebounds from Daniel Hankins-Sanford. Shahid Muhammad had 12 points and three blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
